cross: Cymbidium Redondo Sunset x Cymbidium Gallette

measurements.description: Twenty-one flowers on three upright inflorescences up to 60cm length; sepals yellow suffused burgundy, most intense on superior surface of lateral sepals; petals yellow, burgundy central vein; lip pale yellow striped dark burgundy distally, spotted dark burgundy centrally; anther cap pale yellow; substance very firm; texture matte.
